<h1>Thank you for banking at BankAndTrust.com, <%= @user.first_name %></h1>
<p>
  You have a new update to your account!  </p>

 	<div>
	 	<h3>Your account info is as follows: </h3>
	 	<p>Transaction Date: <%= @account.updated_at %></p>
		<p>Account Number: <%= @account.id  %></p>
		<p>Account Type: <%= @account.account_type %></p>
		<p>Transaction Type: <%= @transaction %></p>
		<p>Amount of Transaction: <%= number_to_currency @amount %></p>
		<p>Previous Balance: <%= number_to_currency @previous_balance %></p>
		<p>Current Balance: <%= number_to_currency @account.balance %></p>
	</div>
<p>To view more info, please visit your banking Dashboard at <%= @url %>. We look forward to doing business with you!</p>


